Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey boys, listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.85,0:00:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans aren’t such a big deal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.14,0:00:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who needs tomorrow anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.39,0:00:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so don’t hide your fists
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.55,0:00:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re not old enough
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to sell your dreams away to uncertainty
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.01,0:00:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey boys, you’re the only ones
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.59,0:00:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who can pull the trigger in your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.59,0:00:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the kids said
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.59,0:00:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re living in this senseless, ridiculous,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.59,0:00:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,awesome world right at this moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.97,0:01:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the kids said
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.47,0:01:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t forget every truth or lie
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.59,0:01:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the kids said
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.89,0:01:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re way too young to die
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.39,0:01:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this empty town lined with empty faces
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.22,0:01:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the kids took off
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.55,0:01:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,into this windless night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.97,0:01:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because they want to change something
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.97,0:01:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, you’ve woken up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.59,0:02:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had a hindrance back then…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.59,0:02:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it won’t be like\Nthat this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.59,0:02:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll show you…\Nthe true power of Sharingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.89,0:02:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine…Then I’ll go all out too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.59,0:02:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You take a good look\Nwith your Sharingan…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.64,0:02:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at my Way of Ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.89,0:02:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow Clone Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.60,0:02:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can’t beat me by just pointlessly…\Nincreasing the number!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You little--!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.26,0:02:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can spot the real body in\None shot with my Sharingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.10,0:02:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I deliberately went along\Nwith your game…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.59,0:03:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t go easy on you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.14,0:03:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Style: Fire Ball Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.85,0:03:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father-Son:\N                       The Broken Crest
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.59,0:04:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was up…\Nwith those eyes of Big Brother’s?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.85,0:04:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn’t…\Njust an ordinary Sharingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.59,0:04:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And…quite a bit of time’s\Npassed since then…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.22,0:04:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but things are still kind of awkward\Nbetween him and Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.18,0:05:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Father…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.59,0:05:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke… how have things\Nbeen going at the Academy lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.14,0:05:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s boring with just school classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.14,0:05:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m always number one, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Style: Fire Ball Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.35,0:05:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wow…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.30,0:06:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the fundamental\NJutsu of the Uchiha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.26,0:06:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sign is as I taught you earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You build up Chakra,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.14,0:06:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stop it once at around between\Nthe mouth and the chest area,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and spew it out at once after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father…is teaching me Jutsu himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.93,0:06:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally… Father has also recognized me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must live up to his expectations!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.59,0:06:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I too can…!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.18,0:06:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Style: Fire Ball Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.39,0:06:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure enough, it won’t go like\Nit did with Itachi, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might’ve still been\Ntoo soon for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.97,0:07:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A member of the Uchiha Clan\Nis not recognized as full-fledged
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.26,0:07:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,until they can use the Fire Style.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.97,0:07:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Uchiha crest…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,means those who possess\Nthe Uchiha that controls fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.43,0:07:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Style: Fire Ball Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Style: Fire Ball Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.05,0:07:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Style: Fire Ball Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.97,0:07:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.01,0:07:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Style: Fire Ball Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.60,0:08:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Style: Fire Ball Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke…!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.59,0:08:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.59,0:08:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What…?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.59,0:08:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh… Don’t move.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.05,0:08:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.14,0:08:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No… It’s nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.39,0:08:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Style: Fire Ball Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure enough, it won’t go\Nlike it did with Itachi, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.93,0:09:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might’ve still been\Ntoo soon for you…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.59,0:09:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m just, getting started.\NDamn it! One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Style: Fire Ball Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.59,0:09:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.10,0:09:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.85,0:09:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:09:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time…\NPlease join me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.59,0:10:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s still too soon for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I were to teach you\Nfor only after a week…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.93,0:10:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not that…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve gotten…the hang of the Jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.59,0:10:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I want you to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.72,0:10:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Failure is not an option!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.64,0:10:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Style: Fire Ball Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.26,0:11:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s my boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’ve done well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.39,0:11:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, improve yourself\Nand soar large
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so as not to bring shame\Nto the crest on your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.97,0:11:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And…let me say one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.05,0:12:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t chase after\Nyour older brother anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.59,0:12:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother…?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.35,0:12:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.39,0:12:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does Father really think of\NBig Brother and me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.55,0:12:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.55,0:12:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other day, Father said to me,\N“That’s my boy.”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He’d always said that only\Nto Big Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.80,0:12:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I was really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.59,0:12:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see…Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.26,0:12:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But lately, Father and Brother\Nhaven’t been getting along, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.59,0:12:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.51,0:13:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I might just be\Na replacement for Big Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your older brother’s your older brother.\NAnd you are you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.64,0:13:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father cares deeply\Nabout you both.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.51,0:13:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why does he only think\Nabout Big Brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.01,0:13:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s not it…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.26,0:13:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father has to protect\Nthe Uchiha Clan
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as a representative of the clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.05,0:13:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.26,0:13:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Itachi is just bigger than you\Nand is your elder.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.68,0:13:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He’ll naturally be entrusted
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.59,0:13:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with that much more work\Nfor the clan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.47,0:13:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father is the supervisor\Nof the work, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.59,0:13:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it might be that his eyes were\Nlikely to go towards your older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, this is just between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.26,0:13:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When he’s with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.59,0:13:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your father does nothing\Nbut talk about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.35,0:14:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s just always sullen\Nand awkward, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll catch up to Big Brother\Nno matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it…!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.89,0:14:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother’s back is still\Nfar out of reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.18,0:15:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, Sasuke…\NMaybe another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.60,0:15:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clan…Clan…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.51,0:15:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You measure incorrectly\Nthe size of your own “vessels”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.22,0:15:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and don’t know the depth of mine,\Nso you grovel there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.22,0:15:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My “vessel” is\Ndismayed at this foolish clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.59,0:15:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like…ever since that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.55,0:15:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he hasn’t been the same\Nas he was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.97,0:15:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, when school’s finished,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.59,0:15:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will you join me for\Nsome Shuriken Jutsu training?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.47,0:16:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m busy.\NYou should have Father teach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.05,0:16:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even I know that you’re better\Nat Shuriken Jutsu than Father is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.64,0:16:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always treat me like\Na nuisance like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, Sasuke.\NMaybe next time…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.59,0:16:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t have the time to\Nbe dealing with you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.68,0:16:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always say, “Forgive me, Sasuke,”\Nand poke me on the forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.51,0:17:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you say “today,”\Nbut it never happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.76,0:17:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness…\Nhe’s the same as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.85,0:17:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.47,0:17:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His eyes looking back\Nat Father that time…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.26,0:17:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn’t just an ordinary Sharingan…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.10,0:17:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.47,0:17:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father…?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.05,0:17:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there several types\Nof Sharingan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.68,0:17:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…You’re already interested\Nin Sharingan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.80,0:17:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, it's still too soon for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.97,0:17:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s totally different from\Nthe Fire Style Jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But someday, I too…!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:18:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all… I’m your kid, so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.59,0:18:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, there is a Visual Jutsu\Nabove the Sharingan,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.64,0:18:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Mangekyo Sharingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.51,0:18:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mangekyo Sharingan…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.93,0:18:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the long history of the Uchiha,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.26,0:18:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it’s a legendary Visual Jutsu\Nthat only a few develop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.59,0:18:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it’s said that it only opened\Nunder a particular condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.59,0:18:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A particular condition…?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.55,0:18:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t chase after your\Nolder brother anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what he thinks of my\Nrelationship with Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.59,0:18:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.59,0:19:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why doesn’t Big Brother care\Nabout me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.18,0:19:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s a bit peculiar…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.59,0:19:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s a type of person who doesn’t\Ncare for making friends with people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.97,0:19:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.64,0:19:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows…?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.89,0:19:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I, his father, can’t read that boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I spoke because I wanted\Nmore of Big Brother’s attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.89,0:19:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father isn’t against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.22,0:19:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Sasuke!\NYour box lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.43,0:19:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll watch your Shuriken practice\Nafter you come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.64,0:19:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not practice, it’s training!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.43,0:19:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s good…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.59,0:19:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not that Father dislikes\NBig Brother, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.47,0:19:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother graduated from the Academy\Nat the top of his class at age seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.14,0:20:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He learned to use\Nthe Sharingan at age eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.64,0:20:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he was promoted\Nto Chunin at age ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.59,0:20:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I’ve got the same Uchiha blood\Nflowing inside me as he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t lose to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.68,0:20:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re not gonna tell me this is\Nthe best you can do, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.55,0:20:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You boast about your Way of Ninja\Nand this is all you've got?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.59,0:20:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still thinking that\NI’m a member of your comrade game?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.05,0:20:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that’s the case, you're…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a hopeless fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.01,0:20:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop wasting time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.97,0:20:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me all you’ve got,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.59,0:20:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you number one hyperactive,\Nknucklehead Ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.22,0:21:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I recalled the parts one by one,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt as though\NI had understood everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.55,0:21:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Faded words which I kept so close to me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.30,0:21:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speechless nights, a hint of warmth,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.55,0:22:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and this distant yearning for you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.76,0:22:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I live, simply repeating this cycle
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.97,0:22:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Held in my two hands\NA droplet of time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.93,0:22:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Softly clutching forgotten memories\NLost words
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.76,0:22:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll keep these thoughts…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.89,0:22:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as Neji said,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.59,0:22:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it seems Sasuke’s in\Nthe darkness right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.47,0:22:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.76,0:22:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He really did hit me with\Nall his might.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.47,0:23:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Sasuke, am I not your comrade\Nor anything anymore?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.76,0:23:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t all those things we\Ndid together in Squad Seven
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.93,0:23:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,mean anything to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.89,0:23:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode,\N“The Secrets of the Mangekyo Sharingan!”
